pagedetails1.title:
SWINBURNE INFO
EVENING
pagedetails1.text: It’s time to stop thinking, start doing, and step into study. Find out all you need to know about our course options and how you can start studying in 2018.

pagedetails2.description:
Yep, exams suck. But you’re nearly there! And we’ve got a couple of things to help get you over the line.

If you need a D&M about your study options for after school, come speak to us at a Swinburne Information Evening.

Or if you just want to knuckle down and get it done, check out these handy exam tips.
